          .border.border-light-gray.center.rounded.mx-auto{style: 'width:240px;height:150px;'}
            .h0.mb0.gray-80.mt1
              %span.strikethrough $99
              %span.h2 /year
            .h2.my0.orange.line-height-1 First year free
            .h3.my0.orange
              = @rolling_date
          .p.gray-30 *No credit card required

    .col.col-12.center.pt2.pb3.sm-py3
      #btn-become-a-member.btn.btn-md.btn-primary.btn-primary--hover Become a member

    .col.col-12
      .max-width-3.mx-auto
        %hr.border-none.border-top--gray
        .p3.center.line-height-2
          .h3.gray-80 “The MyDomino concierge service is exactly what I needed. I wanted to go solar, but I wasn't sure if it made sense. My concierge, Amy, made it easy.”
          .h4.gray-80.pt2 --Julie C., MyDomino member in Sebastopol, CA
  %hr.border-none.border-top--gray

